WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 4=

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:31.050
What's wrong? You're not happy?

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:33.740
Nope.

00:01:34.490 --> 00:01:35.380
I'm happy.

00:01:36.210 --> 00:01:37.540
Just a bit tired.

00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:38.970
Good to hear.

00:01:39.490 --> 00:01:40.540
I was kind of worried

00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:42.660
meeting this crazy bunch
might freak you out.

00:01:43.690 --> 00:01:45.050
Come on, we're not that terrible.

00:01:47.460 --> 00:01:48.570
Do you guys hang out often?

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:49.820
Only once in a while.

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:51.330
Gong and I meet up a lot.

00:01:52.050 --> 00:01:53.770
'Cause if I didn't drag him out,

00:01:53.770 --> 00:01:55.290
he'd stay home all day drawing comics.

00:01:55.770 --> 00:01:57.020
I worry he might burn out.

00:01:57.490 --> 00:01:58.540
I still can't believe

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.460
that's how Gong and Yu He broke up.

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:04.130
Xiaoxi,

00:02:04.820 --> 00:02:07.210
do women just love making wild guesses?

00:02:08.170 --> 00:02:10.660
My boyfriend...He's like

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:12.690
a sly old fox.

00:02:13.100 --> 00:02:14.540
He never really

00:02:14.540 --> 00:02:15.890
cut ties with other girls.

00:02:16.130 --> 00:02:17.850
I just couldn't catch him in the act.

00:02:18.450 --> 00:02:20.170
When a man makes a woman feel unsafe,

00:02:20.820 --> 00:02:22.340
she's gonna get insecure.

00:02:22.450 --> 00:02:23.940
At that time, Yu He really

00:02:24.260 --> 00:02:26.170
was head over heels for Gong.

00:02:26.610 --> 00:02:28.570
But you know what Gong's like.

00:02:28.850 --> 00:02:30.850
Hiring a woman to test him? That's crazy.

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:31.900
Has she gone mad?

00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:34.620
Maybe she didn't

00:02:34.630 --> 00:02:35.730
think it'd actually happen.

00:02:35.940 --> 00:02:38.660
Come on, Gong's no saint.

00:02:38.820 --> 00:02:40.610
It's not about his personality.

00:02:40.980 --> 00:02:42.380
This was bound to happen.

00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:45.820
If I were in his place,

00:02:46.570 --> 00:02:47.690
I'd probably fall for it too.

00:02:48.380 --> 00:02:50.060
Xiaoxi, don't listen to his nonsense.

00:02:50.540 --> 00:02:53.010
Bei's biggest flaw is being too modest.

00:02:56.500 --> 00:02:57.340
He wouldn't.

00:02:57.940 --> 00:02:58.850
I trust him.

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:00.250
Of course, I believe

00:03:00.250 --> 00:03:01.980
you wouldn't test me like that.

00:03:02.260 --> 00:03:03.610
Can you show me the way?

00:03:03.820 --> 00:03:04.820
Don't you recognize me?

00:03:04.820 --> 00:03:06.060
Can we talk for a bit?

00:03:06.220 --> 00:03:07.130
If you need anything,

00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:08.260
I'm up for it.

00:03:10.380 --> 00:03:11.450
But on the other hand,

00:03:11.570 --> 00:03:13.780
this whole thing is a setup.

00:03:14.850 --> 00:03:17.130
Yu He wanted Gong to take the bait.

00:03:19.060 --> 00:03:21.220
You mean she was hoping Gong'd cheat?

00:03:21.380 --> 00:03:22.940
No one wants to be betrayed.

00:03:24.060 --> 00:03:24.900
But when you try to

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:26.340
test how strong a piece of glass is,

00:03:26.980 --> 00:03:29.010
that glass is bound to break.

00:03:30.170 --> 00:03:31.100
In other words,

00:03:31.540 --> 00:03:32.980
once doubt takes root,

00:03:33.570 --> 00:03:34.780
the guilt is already there.

00:03:39.220 --> 00:03:40.980
It's human nature to seek the truth.

00:03:41.570 --> 00:03:42.500
Exposing someone,

00:03:42.980 --> 00:03:44.610
even someone close to you...

00:03:44.890 --> 00:03:46.410
it's understandable.

00:03:47.380 --> 00:03:48.890
But no matter what the motive is,

00:03:49.290 --> 00:03:51.730
for someone who set a trap like Yu He did,

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:53.260
using that kind of trick,

00:03:53.410 --> 00:03:54.690
I think it goes too far.

00:03:55.890 --> 00:03:57.130
But still,

00:03:58.100 --> 00:03:59.260
intentional or not,

00:03:59.450 --> 00:04:01.570
it doesn't change
the fact that Gong cheated.

00:04:01.850 --> 00:04:03.890
The problem is how deliberate it feels.

00:04:05.340 --> 00:04:07.290
You know how the mantis eats its mate?

00:04:08.660 --> 00:04:09.690
From what I know,

00:04:10.010 --> 00:04:11.940
the female mantis eating the male

00:04:13.010 --> 00:04:15.500
is often due to the observer effect.

00:04:17.660 --> 00:04:19.250
Since someone's watching,

00:04:19.250 --> 00:04:20.490
they get overly anxious,

00:04:21.020 --> 00:04:22.850
and mistake the male for a threat.

00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:25.490
And Jiang Yifan

00:04:25.700 --> 00:04:27.610
was the observer in this setup.

00:04:29.780 --> 00:04:31.140
So she's the one

00:04:32.050 --> 00:04:33.810
who really caused this whole mess.

00:04:34.610 --> 00:04:36.460
But if Gong truly loved Yu He,

00:04:37.290 --> 00:04:38.130
Jiang Yifan

00:04:38.140 --> 00:04:39.370
wouldn't have changed anything.

00:04:39.810 --> 00:04:40.700
Suppose

00:04:41.220 --> 00:04:42.340
you were Jiang Yifan,

00:04:42.980 --> 00:04:44.050
how would you seduce Gong?

00:04:49.930 --> 00:04:51.100
Do you have a girlfriend?

00:04:51.370 --> 00:04:52.340
I like you.

00:04:55.410 --> 00:04:57.220
I'm not sure, maybe…

00:04:58.140 --> 00:04:59.610
I wouldn't do anything.

00:04:59.610 --> 00:05:00.850
Let it be a chance encounter.

00:05:00.850 --> 00:05:02.020
See what happens naturally.

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:03.740
See?

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:05.610
You'd be a terrible actress.

00:05:06.660 --> 00:05:07.980
But Jiang Yifan

00:05:08.490 --> 00:05:09.660
nailed the performance.

00:05:10.100 --> 00:05:11.410
Have you ever...

00:05:13.490 --> 00:05:14.980
felt anything for me?

00:05:15.610 --> 00:05:16.610
Even it's

00:05:17.810 --> 00:05:19.050
just a little bit.

00:05:21.100 --> 00:05:22.170
According to Gong,

00:05:22.660 --> 00:05:24.370
she pursued him like crazy...

00:05:24.370 --> 00:05:25.490
like, almost obsessively.

00:05:26.050 --> 00:05:27.290
So imagine this.

00:05:28.050 --> 00:05:30.490
A perfect partner made just for you

00:05:30.730 --> 00:05:32.020
is obsessed with you.

00:05:32.540 --> 00:05:33.810
Honestly, who wouldn't

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:36.170
be tempted?

00:05:37.460 --> 00:05:38.660
Put that way.

00:05:38.930 --> 00:05:40.850
Gong ends up looking like the victim.

00:05:41.540 --> 00:05:42.540
You could say that.

00:05:43.660 --> 00:05:45.730
But the biggest victim in this scheme

00:05:46.780 --> 00:05:47.780
is Yu He.

00:05:48.370 --> 00:05:50.540
From the very beginning,

00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:51.700
Jiang Yifan's motive

00:05:52.140 --> 00:05:53.850
wasn't to test Gong's loyalty,

00:05:54.700 --> 00:05:56.730
but to make Gong fall in love with her.

00:05:57.220 --> 00:05:58.060
No way.

00:06:04.490 --> 00:06:06.170
I mean,

00:06:07.370 --> 00:06:09.220
she have no reason to do that, right?

00:06:09.370 --> 00:06:11.020
If Gong never fell for Jiang Yifan,

00:06:11.540 --> 00:06:12.780
then how could she tell

00:06:12.900 --> 00:06:15.700
whether Gong was too loyal to Yu He,

00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:17.340
or if it was because she

00:06:17.580 --> 00:06:19.410
just wasn't charming or capable enough?

00:06:20.170 --> 00:06:21.370
So Jiang Yifan

00:06:21.700 --> 00:06:23.250
boldly confessed, took the lead,

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:25.410
just to prove herself,

00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:27.780
to show her worth in this whole scheme.

00:06:28.850 --> 00:06:30.810
With the pass of a legitimate mistress,

00:06:31.220 --> 00:06:33.490
she played on men's worst instincts at will.

00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:37.370
(It's not what you think.)

00:06:38.050 --> 00:06:38.980
(It's not.)

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:40.540
This Jiang Yifan's

00:06:40.730 --> 00:06:42.930
honestly such a despicable woman.

00:06:49.980 --> 00:06:51.050
You had a long day.

00:06:51.340 --> 00:06:52.900
Go home and get some rest.

00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:53.740
Ah.

00:06:54.340 --> 00:06:56.410
You don't have to walk me up. I'm fine.

00:06:57.410 --> 00:06:58.580
Go see Sen off instead.

00:07:01.660 --> 00:07:02.850
You okay?

00:07:03.700 --> 00:07:04.540
Yeah.

00:07:06.380 --> 00:07:07.220
Okay.

00:07:07.220 --> 00:07:08.900
Get some good sleep tonight.

00:07:09.930 --> 00:07:10.810
Drive safe.

00:07:12.290 --> 00:07:13.130
I'm heading out.

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:15.500
Bei.

00:07:16.610 --> 00:07:17.450
I love you.

00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:24.740
I know.

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:30.610
Then I'm going.

00:07:30.610 --> 00:07:31.450
Alright.

00:07:31.760 --> 00:07:33.450
Bye.

00:07:57.700 --> 00:07:58.540
Hey, Sen.

00:08:01.020 --> 00:08:01.930
Here's the thing.

00:08:03.050 --> 00:08:03.890
Go ahead.

00:08:04.410 --> 00:08:06.580
If you saw Li Xiaoxi with someone else,

00:08:07.810 --> 00:08:09.540
would you tell me?

00:08:09.660 --> 00:08:10.580
Do you need to ask?

00:08:11.100 --> 00:08:11.980
Of course I would.

00:08:13.170 --> 00:08:14.290
What if I'd be hurt?

00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:16.410
Better than letting others
think you're a fool.

00:08:16.930 --> 00:08:18.020
You're my buddy.

00:08:18.810 --> 00:08:19.900
So what you mean is...

00:08:20.900 --> 00:08:22.340
keeping quiet when you know it

00:08:22.850 --> 00:08:23.930
makes you an accomplice?

00:08:24.290 --> 00:08:25.140
Pretty much.

00:08:30.100 --> 00:08:31.100
Why are you asking?

00:08:34.100 --> 00:08:34.940
Sen.

00:08:35.580 --> 00:08:36.850
- Actually...
- Is it Mingming?

00:08:40.460 --> 00:08:41.300
Yeah.

00:08:43.220 --> 00:08:44.300
Maybe you should drop it.

00:08:45.060 --> 00:08:46.530
Mingming might be a nice girl,

00:08:46.770 --> 00:08:49.010
but I don't think she's right for you.

00:08:49.010 --> 00:08:50.010
I know that guy.

00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:51.940
Bei.

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:52.850
Trust me on this.

00:08:53.370 --> 00:08:54.460
I know exactly what kind

00:08:54.460 --> 00:08:55.700
of person Mingming is.

00:08:55.700 --> 00:08:56.700
I trust you.

00:08:56.700 --> 00:08:57.820
But you have to trust me too.

00:08:58.060 --> 00:08:59.180
What I saw... it's not

00:08:59.180 --> 00:09:00.220
as simple as you think.

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:01.610
I told you. I know her.

00:09:02.300 --> 00:09:03.770
Not every relationship

00:09:04.010 --> 00:09:05.250
has to follow the rules.

00:09:05.370 --> 00:09:06.250
She has her thoughts.

00:09:06.250 --> 00:09:07.820
I respect that, and I understand her.

00:09:08.490 --> 00:09:10.370
I just hope she can
end things with that guy

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:11.850
openly and honestly.

00:09:17.650 --> 00:09:19.420
Can you not treat me like everyone else,

00:09:20.220 --> 00:09:21.250
as if I were just some

00:09:21.650 --> 00:09:23.010
clueless fool kept in the dark?

00:09:23.220 --> 00:09:25.130
I'm your buddy.
I just want what's best for you.

00:09:26.820 --> 00:09:28.250
Fine. Maybe I'm overthinking it.

00:09:31.180 --> 00:09:34.250
I know you're trying to help.
I'm not blaming you.

00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:41.250
Just don't tell Gong and the others, okay?

00:09:43.180 --> 00:09:44.220
They're not like you.

00:09:45.370 --> 00:09:46.220
Don't worry.

00:09:46.610 --> 00:09:47.700
I won't tell them.

00:09:48.890 --> 00:09:49.730
Thanks.

00:09:51.060 --> 00:09:52.100
Just make sure…

00:09:53.890 --> 00:09:54.890
you know your doing.

00:10:10.220 --> 00:10:11.420
So this Jiang Yifan

00:10:11.770 --> 00:10:13.490
boldly confessed, took the lead,

00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:15.460
just to prove herself,

00:10:15.730 --> 00:10:17.770
to show her worth in this whole scheme.

00:10:18.130 --> 00:10:20.100
With the pass of a legitimate mistress,

00:10:20.490 --> 00:10:22.770
she played on men's worst instincts at will.

00:10:23.220 --> 00:10:25.300
You could say Jiang Yifan
feels no guilt at all,

00:10:25.530 --> 00:10:27.100
nor any sense of shame.

00:10:27.580 --> 00:10:28.940
This Jiang Yifan's

00:10:29.460 --> 00:10:31.940
honestly such a despicable woman.

00:10:46.100 --> 00:10:48.100
(Taxi)
Sir, please wait here a moment.

00:11:04.650 --> 00:11:05.850
I'm here. Go back now.

00:11:08.010 --> 00:11:08.980
Go on home then.

00:11:09.580 --> 00:11:11.180
No need to text me once you get home.

00:11:11.300 --> 00:11:12.460
You might get into trouble.

00:11:14.010 --> 00:11:14.850
Then…

00:11:15.010 --> 00:11:16.220
let me know when you're home.

00:11:17.220 --> 00:11:18.340
I'm telling you right now.

00:11:18.580 --> 00:11:19.890
I'm totally fine. Don't worry.

00:11:24.490 --> 00:11:25.980
How am I supposed to treat you?

00:11:27.130 --> 00:11:29.010
You've already been so, so good to me.

00:11:30.010 --> 00:11:31.850
I'm really, truly content.

00:11:40.250 --> 00:11:41.180
Don't look back.

00:11:42.490 --> 00:11:43.650
I think she might've seen us.

00:11:56.370 --> 00:11:57.610
Maybe I just imagined it.

00:11:59.180 --> 00:12:00.020
Don't overthink it.

00:12:02.530 --> 00:12:04.460
I'm leaving now. Take care of yourself.

00:12:14.460 --> 00:12:15.420
Let's go, sir.

00:12:25.770 --> 00:12:26.610
Miss,

00:12:27.890 --> 00:12:30.340
was that your boyfriend just now?

00:12:32.580 --> 00:12:33.530
Sort of.

00:12:37.370 --> 00:12:39.340
Usually the guy sends the girl home.

00:12:39.530 --> 00:12:40.530
But you...

00:12:41.300 --> 00:12:42.610
sent your boyfriend home instead.

00:12:45.850 --> 00:12:47.300
I want to spend more time with him.

00:12:48.420 --> 00:12:49.650
Why not just live together?

00:12:50.370 --> 00:12:51.300
It's not convenient.

00:12:54.060 --> 00:12:55.220
His workplace is far?

00:12:56.420 --> 00:12:57.300
No, that's not it.

00:12:58.060 --> 00:12:59.130
I don't want to be the one

00:12:59.890 --> 00:13:01.530
always by his side, every day.

00:13:02.250 --> 00:13:03.490
You don't want to get married?

00:13:04.650 --> 00:13:05.490
Married?

00:13:11.370 --> 00:13:13.420
I think I'm more scared of it.

00:13:14.370 --> 00:13:16.130
I just don't get you young people.

00:13:34.220 --> 00:13:36.420
(Mud Buddha)

00:13:36.420 --> 00:13:38.650
(Jiang Yifan, I miss you.)

00:13:42.220 --> 00:13:43.610
(I thought I could forget you.)

00:13:44.010 --> 00:13:45.770
(But I underestimated how deeply I love you.)

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:52.460
(I wish we hadn't met that way)

00:13:52.460 --> 00:13:53.460
(we did.)

00:13:57.420 --> 00:13:59.460
(A meeting destined to end in parting.)

00:13:59.980 --> 00:14:01.850
(I don't know when I'll ever get over it.)

00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:17.300
(Jiang Yifan.)

00:14:17.890 --> 00:14:19.220
(I think I saw you today.)

00:14:24.730 --> 00:14:25.570
Jiang Yifan.

00:14:27.730 --> 00:14:28.580
Who are you?

00:14:28.580 --> 00:14:29.460
(But...)

00:14:29.890 --> 00:14:31.700
(I wish it wasn't when I was wasted.)

00:14:31.970 --> 00:14:32.820
I was mistaken.

00:14:32.820 --> 00:14:34.460
(Sometimes I feels like we're just)

00:14:35.530 --> 00:14:37.220
(in a long-distance, lagged relationship.)

00:14:38.130 --> 00:14:39.300
(It's not there's no love.)

00:14:39.940 --> 00:14:41.060
(It's just beyond control.)

00:14:43.130 --> 00:14:44.340
(How are you doing now?)

00:14:45.650 --> 00:14:46.490
(Seeing someone?)

00:14:48.460 --> 00:14:49.850
(I admit I'd rather not know.)

00:14:50.340 --> 00:14:51.340
(I'd feel jealous.)

00:14:52.420 --> 00:14:54.100
(No one's good enough for you in my heart.)

00:14:56.730 --> 00:14:57.650
(Jiang Yifan.)

00:14:58.250 --> 00:15:00.340
(Jiang Yifan.)

00:15:01.490 --> 00:15:03.010
(I can't help thinking about you.)

00:15:03.730 --> 00:15:05.180
(And you'll never know.)

00:15:06.980 --> 00:15:07.980
(Was)

00:15:09.010 --> 00:15:09.940
(that you today?)

00:15:10.610 --> 00:15:12.180
I've been reading your comics lately.

00:15:12.180 --> 00:15:13.460
Why'd you change your name?

00:15:14.650 --> 00:15:15.530
It's because

00:15:18.060 --> 00:15:19.460
Mud Buddha can't cross the river.

00:15:21.980 --> 00:15:22.820
It's because

00:15:22.940 --> 00:15:24.530
Mud Buddha can't cross the river.

00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:40.370
(I want to talk to you.)

00:15:48.460 --> 00:15:49.730
(Mud Buddha)
(I'm free right now.)

00:15:53.130 --> 00:15:54.010
(Jiang Yifan)
(Where are you?)

00:15:56.060 --> 00:15:56.900
(Mud Buddha)
(Home.)

00:15:57.370 --> 00:15:58.420
(Can you still find it?)

00:16:01.700 --> 00:16:02.810
(Jiang Yifan)
(I'll come pick you up.)

00:16:06.250 --> 00:16:07.090
(Mud Buddha)
(Alright.)

00:17:11.700 --> 00:17:13.250
(Do you have to be this cool?)

00:17:13.770 --> 00:17:14.860
(Jiang Yifan.)

00:17:43.900 --> 00:17:44.860
Anyone home?

00:17:47.290 --> 00:17:48.130
I'm here.

00:17:52.380 --> 00:17:53.250
Long time no see.

00:17:54.620 --> 00:17:55.460
Long time no see.

00:17:57.940 --> 00:17:58.780
Let's go.

00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:00.460
Sure.

00:18:07.620 --> 00:18:08.530
Nice ride.

00:18:13.810 --> 00:18:14.730
Hop on.

00:18:15.010 --> 00:18:15.850
I'll take you.

00:18:17.380 --> 00:18:18.220
You know how to ride?

00:18:18.620 --> 00:18:19.530
Are you kidding?

00:18:19.860 --> 00:18:21.380
I used to race down Bamian Mountain.

00:18:21.620 --> 00:18:22.940
I've got a reputation.

00:18:23.620 --> 00:18:24.940
Come on, get on.

00:18:25.330 --> 00:18:26.380
I know a place

00:18:26.700 --> 00:18:28.180
of good food. I'll take you there.

00:18:30.700 --> 00:18:31.570
Get on already.

00:18:40.940 --> 00:18:42.090
Hold on tight.

00:18:42.570 --> 00:18:43.570
When I speed up,

00:18:43.570 --> 00:18:45.380
it can make time rewind.

00:18:46.420 --> 00:18:48.140
(Then let time rewind to)

00:18:48.420 --> 00:18:49.900
(before I met you.)

00:19:29.380 --> 00:19:30.620
Time rewind, huh?

00:19:34.290 --> 00:19:35.810
I really wish it could rewind to

00:19:35.810 --> 00:19:37.050
before I got on this bike.

00:19:55.980 --> 00:19:56.820
Gong.

00:19:57.330 --> 00:19:58.170
What did you say?

00:19:59.770 --> 00:20:01.660
The reason I came to see you today is...

00:20:02.090 --> 00:20:03.090
Jiang Yifan.

00:20:04.330 --> 00:20:05.860
Aren't you rushing it a bit too much?

00:20:06.620 --> 00:20:08.620
I know exactly why you came to me.

00:20:09.140 --> 00:20:11.330
But can we just put all stresses aside

00:20:11.330 --> 00:20:12.290
for a while now?

00:20:12.620 --> 00:20:14.730
Old friends meeting after a long time.

00:20:14.730 --> 00:20:16.010
Let's catch up first.

00:20:17.980 --> 00:20:19.090
Catching up can wait.

00:20:19.980 --> 00:20:21.250
First, promise me one thing.

00:20:22.090 --> 00:20:23.940
I can promise you anything.

00:20:25.330 --> 00:20:26.900
But I have one condition.

00:20:28.730 --> 00:20:29.570
Go ahead.

00:20:31.140 --> 00:20:32.700
Last time, you just walked away

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:35.490
and disappeared for so long.

00:20:36.010 --> 00:20:36.900
So,

00:20:37.530 --> 00:20:38.620
stay with me tonight.

00:20:40.980 --> 00:20:41.820
Your hand.

00:20:52.090 --> 00:20:54.010
Sir, you're still driving this late?

00:20:55.420 --> 00:20:56.260
Yeah.

00:20:57.290 --> 00:20:58.290
My wife's

00:20:59.380 --> 00:21:00.380
probably asleep by now.

00:21:02.250 --> 00:21:04.810
I take a few more rides for more money.

00:21:05.900 --> 00:21:08.290
Has she ever complained you're too busy?

00:21:08.570 --> 00:21:10.010
Complained? About what?

00:21:10.570 --> 00:21:11.980
We don't overthink things.

00:21:11.980 --> 00:21:13.980
Life is just the daily grind.

00:21:14.420 --> 00:21:16.700
But love shouldn't be only about that.

00:21:19.530 --> 00:21:21.770
I don't want dating to turn into living.

00:21:22.180 --> 00:21:24.180
Dating, living...

00:21:24.460 --> 00:21:25.330
Honestly,

00:21:26.090 --> 00:21:27.140
it's the same thing.

00:21:28.330 --> 00:21:29.570
I don't think so.

00:21:31.770 --> 00:21:33.220
Dating is wonderful.

00:21:34.700 --> 00:21:36.570
Every day feels like being a kid.

00:21:37.420 --> 00:21:39.050
Everything you do together is fun.

00:21:47.900 --> 00:21:49.980
You fear losing that person,

00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:53.330
so you treasure every moment even more.

00:21:57.050 --> 00:21:58.460
Living together is different.

00:22:00.180 --> 00:22:02.050
Time only makes two people

00:22:02.050 --> 00:22:03.860
show their worst sides to each other.

00:22:05.460 --> 00:22:07.290
The things you once found cute

00:22:07.570 --> 00:22:09.180
would become things driving you crazy.

00:22:09.860 --> 00:22:11.860
You start arguing over anything,

00:22:12.220 --> 00:22:14.770
not worrying about hurting each other.

00:22:15.010 --> 00:22:17.420
It's like marriage gives you that privilege.

00:22:19.660 --> 00:22:20.500
Sir,

00:22:21.010 --> 00:22:22.380
have you regretted getting married?

00:22:27.090 --> 00:22:28.010
Of course I have.

00:22:28.810 --> 00:22:30.620
I've regretted it many times.

00:22:31.250 --> 00:22:34.090
Every time we fight, I start thinking,

00:22:36.420 --> 00:22:37.460
how did I end up with

00:22:37.460 --> 00:22:39.570
such an unreasonable woman?

00:22:40.460 --> 00:22:42.490
Was I blind back then?

00:22:44.050 --> 00:22:44.940
Then I think,

00:22:45.810 --> 00:22:46.980
she's probably the same.

00:22:47.460 --> 00:22:48.330
Maybe she is.

00:22:50.380 --> 00:22:51.220
And look,

00:22:51.700 --> 00:22:52.770
while we were talking,

00:22:52.900 --> 00:22:54.180
she finished cooking the meal

00:22:54.380 --> 00:22:55.530
and put it in front of me.

00:22:58.050 --> 00:22:59.490
Have you ever thought,

00:22:59.900 --> 00:23:01.420
maybe you just need her?

00:23:02.660 --> 00:23:04.860
If two people are only together because

00:23:04.860 --> 00:23:06.250
they need each other,

00:23:07.330 --> 00:23:08.570
isn't it kind of pathetic?

00:23:09.530 --> 00:23:10.770
Doesn't being together means

00:23:12.250 --> 00:23:13.660
they need each other?

00:23:17.460 --> 00:23:18.460
All I know is,

00:23:19.220 --> 00:23:20.220
if you love someone,

00:23:20.980 --> 00:23:22.620
you should make them happy.

00:23:24.140 --> 00:23:25.460
I don't need anything in return.

00:23:28.220 --> 00:23:29.060
Oh no.

00:23:30.290 --> 00:23:31.130
Miss,

00:23:31.770 --> 00:23:33.330
look, got so caught up talking

00:23:33.330 --> 00:23:34.460
I took the wrong path.

00:23:36.180 --> 00:23:37.020
Well,

00:23:37.810 --> 00:23:39.940
I'll stop the meter. No more charges.

00:23:40.180 --> 00:23:41.530
And I'll drive you home, okay?

00:23:41.530 --> 00:23:43.050
It's fine. Don't worry about it.

00:23:45.770 --> 00:23:47.250
Alright, thank you.

00:23:47.380 --> 00:23:48.220
Miss.

00:23:48.860 --> 00:23:49.700
It's okay.

00:24:06.460 --> 00:24:08.380
You've known Bei for years, right?

00:24:08.860 --> 00:24:10.460
You know Bei? Jiang Yifan.

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:11.810
What a small world.

00:24:13.730 --> 00:24:14.810
Don't make that face.

00:24:16.140 --> 00:24:17.330
This ice cream is amazing.

00:24:17.330 --> 00:24:18.250
Here, have a bite.

00:24:18.770 --> 00:24:20.490
No. Seeing you kinda kills my appetite.

00:24:20.490 --> 00:24:21.700
You haven't even tried.

00:24:21.700 --> 00:24:22.590
Untouched. Try it.

00:24:22.600 --> 00:24:23.530
I said I don't want it.

00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:25.330
Last time you still called me baby.

00:24:25.330 --> 00:24:26.290
Hello!

00:24:26.860 --> 00:24:27.700
Hello!

00:24:29.140 --> 00:24:31.330
May I ask you a few questions?

00:24:32.090 --> 00:24:34.050
My girlfriend's a little shy.

00:24:34.050 --> 00:24:35.150
- Just ask me.
- Who's your girlfriend?

00:24:35.470 --> 00:24:36.330
Oh, I see.

00:24:36.330 --> 00:24:38.050
I thought you took us for

00:24:38.050 --> 00:24:38.890
some creeps.

00:24:39.330 --> 00:24:40.460
You kinda look like it.

00:24:41.940 --> 00:24:42.900
So, you guys are...

00:24:43.380 --> 00:24:45.050
Have you seen our show, "Love or Not"?

00:24:45.050 --> 00:24:46.530
It's produced by our team.

00:24:47.090 --> 00:24:47.980
Oh, I've watched it.

00:24:47.980 --> 00:24:48.850
I recognize you.

00:24:48.860 --> 00:24:50.660
- You're the pretty one.
- Stop it already.

00:24:50.660 --> 00:24:52.180
Their questions go way out of line.

00:24:52.620 --> 00:24:53.460
You want to interview me?

00:24:53.810 --> 00:24:54.660
Yeah, that's right.

00:24:54.660 --> 00:24:55.980
But hey, no need to be nervous.

00:24:56.180 --> 00:24:57.940
Answer however you want.

00:24:58.620 --> 00:25:00.090
I'll dare to answer anything,

00:25:00.330 --> 00:25:01.620
as long as you dare to air it.

00:25:01.940 --> 00:25:03.490
Enough talk. Let's go.

00:25:04.490 --> 00:25:05.420
Sorry.

00:25:05.420 --> 00:25:06.570
Can we be blurred out?

00:25:09.250 --> 00:25:11.570
Looks like you two have quite a story.

00:25:12.770 --> 00:25:14.770
- Alright, let's get started.
- Blur them.

00:25:15.050 --> 00:25:15.940
First question.

00:25:15.940 --> 00:25:18.330
How long have you been together?

00:25:19.050 --> 00:25:20.010
A little over a year.

00:25:20.290 --> 00:25:21.940
But she did leave me for a while.

00:25:22.530 --> 00:25:23.770
You know, girls can be a bit

00:25:23.770 --> 00:25:24.620
willful sometimes.

00:25:24.770 --> 00:25:25.940
Maybe I spoiled her too much.

00:25:26.180 --> 00:25:27.860
Luckily, she came back to me in the end.

00:25:28.380 --> 00:25:30.140
Guess that's what fate is.

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:32.620
So losing her and getting her back

00:25:33.010 --> 00:25:34.810
made you cherish her more, right?

00:25:34.940 --> 00:25:35.780
Exactly.

00:25:36.460 --> 00:25:38.770
We both realized the other person

00:25:38.770 --> 00:25:40.330
means the most to us.

00:25:40.900 --> 00:25:41.740
Do you still remember

00:25:41.860 --> 00:25:43.420
what was the most unforgettable moment

00:25:43.420 --> 00:25:44.260
between you two?

00:25:44.420 --> 00:25:45.730
Have you heard this saying?

00:25:46.420 --> 00:25:47.700
I want to be with her,

00:25:47.980 --> 00:25:49.380
and she wants to be with me.

00:25:49.380 --> 00:25:50.380
We both know

00:25:50.380 --> 00:25:51.940
one day we'll be together.

00:25:52.330 --> 00:25:53.180
But we don't know

00:25:53.180 --> 00:25:54.770
when that exact day

00:25:54.770 --> 00:25:55.770
will come.

00:25:56.140 --> 00:25:57.770
That's the most beautiful part.

00:25:58.730 --> 00:26:00.010
You're really straight-forward.

00:26:00.010 --> 00:26:00.890
So, what did she say

00:26:00.890 --> 00:26:02.490
that moved you the most?

00:26:04.010 --> 00:26:04.940
One time,

00:26:05.290 --> 00:26:07.490
she looked at me seriously and said...

00:26:07.980 --> 00:26:10.010
I'm sure you're the right one for me.

00:26:11.530 --> 00:26:12.420
I've fallen for you.

00:26:14.660 --> 00:26:16.220
So romantic.

00:26:16.570 --> 00:26:17.420
So,

00:26:17.770 --> 00:26:19.570
she's pursued you?

00:26:19.940 --> 00:26:21.180
No, I pursued her.

00:26:22.570 --> 00:26:23.460
Do you love her?

00:26:23.900 --> 00:26:24.900
Let me put it this way.

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:28.140
As long as she's happy,

00:26:28.330 --> 00:26:30.380
even if it means I have to suffer,

00:26:30.530 --> 00:26:31.530
I'm fine with that.

00:26:32.700 --> 00:26:33.540
Dude,

00:26:33.810 --> 00:26:34.900
you studied liberal arts?

00:26:35.730 --> 00:26:37.290
That question's way out of my league.

00:26:38.770 --> 00:26:40.460
Anyway, wish you two happiness.

00:26:44.810 --> 00:26:45.940
We'll catch you next time.

00:26:46.460 --> 00:26:47.420
What would you like?

00:26:47.530 --> 00:26:48.620
What do you usually like?

00:26:51.010 --> 00:26:51.940
Whatever's fine.

00:26:51.940 --> 00:26:52.940
Wow, great choice.

00:26:53.250 --> 00:26:55.140
That's their best seller.

00:26:55.460 --> 00:26:56.570
Two of "Whatever", then.

00:26:56.730 --> 00:26:57.730
Okay, coming right up.

00:27:02.530 --> 00:27:03.660
How have you been?

00:27:04.700 --> 00:27:05.540
Pretty good.

00:27:06.420 --> 00:27:07.260
You?

00:27:08.220 --> 00:27:09.060
Same old.

00:27:09.380 --> 00:27:10.700
Still living on my own.

00:27:11.460 --> 00:27:12.980
My ex, though...

00:27:13.250 --> 00:27:14.660
she's been on and off.

00:27:15.730 --> 00:27:16.570
Yu He?

00:27:18.290 --> 00:27:20.980
Still as recklessly devoted as ever.

00:27:22.810 --> 00:27:23.650
Thanks.

00:27:26.010 --> 00:27:26.850
Thanks.

00:27:28.490 --> 00:27:29.730
I've always been curious.

00:27:31.530 --> 00:27:32.980
How did you meet Mr. Bei?

00:27:36.620 --> 00:27:37.570
At a bar.

00:27:38.490 --> 00:27:39.420
A bar?

00:27:41.010 --> 00:27:43.010
But Bei never goes to bars.

00:27:45.570 --> 00:27:46.410
Bei,

00:27:46.900 --> 00:27:49.420
tonight I'm letting my true self shine.

00:27:49.530 --> 00:27:51.490
Let's hit the Night Club together.

00:27:51.660 --> 00:27:54.420
I'll meet you there in half an hour.

00:27:54.980 --> 00:27:55.820
(Bei)

00:28:16.810 --> 00:28:17.980
Still delaying the draft.

00:28:18.900 --> 00:28:20.770
If you don't deliver it today,

00:28:21.860 --> 00:28:22.810
I'm living here tonight.

00:28:23.730 --> 00:28:25.050
Bei... Bei,

00:28:25.810 --> 00:28:28.770
I can't let my true self shine today.

00:28:29.220 --> 00:28:30.490
What true self?

00:28:30.490 --> 00:28:32.460
Aren't you yourself right now?

00:28:32.620 --> 00:28:33.490
Yeah, yeah.

00:28:33.490 --> 00:28:35.220
Anyway, good luck.

00:28:35.420 --> 00:28:36.940
Your drinks are on me.

00:28:36.940 --> 00:28:38.250
Seriously, look at yourself.

00:28:38.250 --> 00:28:39.090
I'll pay for it.

00:28:40.380 --> 00:28:42.700
Now hurry up and draw. I beg you.

00:28:42.980 --> 00:28:44.050
You have no idea how many

00:28:44.050 --> 00:28:45.900
crises I shield you from every day.

00:28:47.250 --> 00:28:48.090
What's wrong?

00:28:48.860 --> 00:28:51.940
How did I end up being your matchmaker?

00:28:51.940 --> 00:28:53.570
Ugh.

00:28:54.180 --> 00:28:57.490
Why did Joyce have to show up that day?

00:28:58.900 --> 00:29:01.050
Missing deadlines just messes things up.

00:29:05.220 --> 00:29:06.320
(Convenience Store)
I'll take these.

00:29:06.380 --> 00:29:07.420
Instant noodles again?

00:29:08.050 --> 00:29:09.180
Why not try something else?

00:29:09.660 --> 00:29:10.500
I'm used to it.

00:29:10.510 --> 00:29:11.390
Oh, right.

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.810
The chocolate you asked for arrived.

00:29:13.330 --> 00:29:14.620
Still one of each flavor?

00:29:16.290 --> 00:29:17.290
Yeah, thanks.

00:29:22.060 --> 00:29:24.660
(Did you go to bed?)

00:29:24.730 --> 00:29:25.570
(Are you sleeping?)

00:29:27.460 --> 00:29:28.810
How did Yu He even find you?

00:29:29.700 --> 00:29:30.660
She didn't tell you?

00:29:30.660 --> 00:29:31.500
No.

00:29:34.900 --> 00:29:36.290
I help a lot of girls

00:29:36.460 --> 00:29:37.770
test their boyfriends.

00:29:41.330 --> 00:29:42.660
Why would you do that?

00:29:43.860 --> 00:29:44.860
Maybe it's because

00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:46.980
I've seen too much

00:29:46.980 --> 00:29:48.290
betrayal in love these years.

00:29:49.940 --> 00:29:51.940
Plenty of guys act all lovey-dovey

00:29:51.940 --> 00:29:52.980
with their girlfriends,

00:29:53.660 --> 00:29:55.900
but they'd flirt with other girls secretly.

00:29:56.810 --> 00:29:57.860
This is my boyfriend.

00:29:57.860 --> 00:29:58.980
Zhou Xiaolong from Class 3.

00:29:59.330 --> 00:30:00.530
- Hi.
- Hi.

00:30:00.530 --> 00:30:02.290
Xiaolong, this is my roommate.

00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:03.940
My best friend, Li Xiaoxi.

00:30:04.090 --> 00:30:05.770
Her business is my business.

00:30:07.420 --> 00:30:09.140
If you ever need help with heavy stuff,

00:30:09.600 --> 00:30:10.450
just let me know.

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:11.300
Yeah.

00:30:11.300 --> 00:30:12.940
Things like carrying water,

00:30:13.180 --> 00:30:14.290
just leave them to Xiaolong.

00:30:16.770 --> 00:30:18.460
Oh right, how about...

00:30:18.810 --> 00:30:19.990
(Xiaolong)
we add each other on WeChat.

00:30:20.700 --> 00:30:22.220
Xiaolong, have you eaten?

00:30:22.940 --> 00:30:24.660
How can you not eat?

00:30:25.700 --> 00:30:27.700
I'm actually with Xiaoxi right now.

00:30:27.900 --> 00:30:29.140
Let's grab food together later.

00:30:31.220 --> 00:30:32.060
Mm.

00:30:32.980 --> 00:30:33.860
You missed me?

00:30:35.330 --> 00:30:36.660
- I missed you too.
- (What are you up to?)

00:30:36.660 --> 00:30:38.660
(Zhou Xiaolong)
(I miss you. Let's eat together.)

00:30:38.770 --> 00:30:39.610
What should we eat?

00:30:40.330 --> 00:30:41.730
At first, I didn't get involved.

00:30:43.060 --> 00:30:43.940
But guys like that

00:30:43.940 --> 00:30:45.420
are like ticking time bombs.

00:30:46.090 --> 00:30:48.010
Over time, the girls around him

00:30:48.570 --> 00:30:50.290
end up getting hurt all over.

00:30:51.380 --> 00:30:52.900
Why'd you go running without eating?

00:30:52.900 --> 00:30:54.090
No wonder you felt dizzy.

00:30:54.660 --> 00:30:55.810
- Here, have a cookie.
- Xi.

00:30:57.420 --> 00:30:58.770
Do I look fat?

00:31:00.900 --> 00:31:01.810
You're not fat at all.

00:31:02.490 --> 00:31:03.940
Then why is Xiaolong suddenly

00:31:04.330 --> 00:31:05.570
acting so cold to me?

00:31:06.900 --> 00:31:08.810
He hardly replies to my texts lately.

00:31:10.730 --> 00:31:12.460
I must've made him upset somehow.

00:31:13.530 --> 00:31:14.730
He once said

00:31:15.490 --> 00:31:16.770
my face looked a bit chubby.

00:31:18.330 --> 00:31:19.170
Or maybe…

00:31:20.570 --> 00:31:21.860
I get too attached,

00:31:23.050 --> 00:31:24.980
and Xiaolong's sick of me.

00:31:28.290 --> 00:31:29.290
You did nothing wrong.

00:31:29.290 --> 00:31:31.330
Why keep blaming yourself for it?

00:31:31.570 --> 00:31:32.700
It must be my fault.

00:31:33.090 --> 00:31:34.530
Why do victims doubt themselves...

00:31:34.530 --> 00:31:35.370
It must be my fault.

00:31:36.090 --> 00:31:37.140
and live with the pain?

00:31:38.050 --> 00:31:39.700
You finally agreed to see me.

00:31:41.570 --> 00:31:43.220
Why do you keep asking me out?

00:31:46.140 --> 00:31:47.730
Do you really not get it?

00:31:49.330 --> 00:31:51.140
But you're Xiaowei's boyfriend.

00:31:51.490 --> 00:31:53.900
I know this isn't fair to Xiaowei.

00:31:54.480 --> 00:31:55.330
But…

00:31:55.330 --> 00:31:57.250
But love isn't about fairness.

00:31:57.490 --> 00:31:58.490
The first time I saw you,

00:31:58.490 --> 00:31:59.660
I fell for you right away.

00:32:03.660 --> 00:32:05.620
I've wanted to break up with her,

00:32:06.140 --> 00:32:07.140
but I feared to hurt her.

00:32:07.140 --> 00:32:08.220
So I haven't said it.

00:32:08.530 --> 00:32:09.380
But don't worry,

00:32:09.700 --> 00:32:11.140
I'll break up with her

00:32:11.420 --> 00:32:12.260
right away.

00:32:17.250 --> 00:32:18.700
Xiaowei…

00:32:19.420 --> 00:32:20.260
Only by exposing

00:32:20.380 --> 00:32:22.180
that guy's true side in front of her,

00:32:22.700 --> 00:32:23.900
will she finally wake up.

00:32:24.810 --> 00:32:25.810
As you wish,

00:32:27.050 --> 00:32:28.250
we're done.

00:32:29.010 --> 00:32:29.850
Get out.

00:32:33.730 --> 00:32:35.860
I hate seeing so many girls get hurt.

00:32:36.940 --> 00:32:37.980
So I decided

00:32:38.330 --> 00:32:39.940
to expose the cheaters in love

00:32:40.980 --> 00:32:42.900
and help those girls get out sooner.

00:32:48.500 --> 00:32:50.300
(Cheater)

00:32:56.140 --> 00:32:57.940
What happened to all those

00:32:57.940 --> 00:32:59.010
couples you tested?

00:32:59.420 --> 00:33:00.490
Most of them broke up.

00:33:05.620 --> 00:33:07.250
You're like a demon-revealing mirror,

